From 3a63f4665dc6bf43e7a638fbfc4b63cd848d9d9f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sidhanta Sahu <sidhanta.sahu@oss.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 29 Jul 2025 10:42:44 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 24/24] UPSTREAM:CP:wifi:ath12K: Enhance wmi ctrl stats

- Add new wmi debug list - period_wmi_list for storing the
periodic event
- Use existing wmi_list for on-demand stats
- Add tagid under struct wmi_ctrl_path_stats_to print the
specific stats from the un-freed list
- Re-factor the print function of all wmi ctrl stats to work
with this new change

Patch-dependency:
0462-22-QSDK-CP-wifi-ath12k-Fix-crash-while-handling-pmlo-st.patch

Signed-off-by: Sidhanta Sahu <sidhanta.sahu@oss.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Arpitha Ramesha <arpirame@qti.qualcomm.com>
